    "body": "Note that we already throttle signatures for checking if we're the aggregator for a slot in `ExternalSigner`.  We should probably update `signValidatorRegistration` to add tasks to the `taskQueue` so it uses the same throttling.  Not sure if the upstream code needs to be updated to send registrations in batches or something rather than waiting for all signatures to complete given they could take some time now.",
